metadata.name: Aeon
metadata.description:
“Long periods of time” (Cambridge Dictionary, 2022)  At 310 metres, Varso Tower is the same height as the EUs ex-tallest building, the shard. Newly constructed, Varso Tower now claims the spot as the tallest building in the EU for the foreseeable future.
 
To have experienced such a behemoth of a location will remain a proud achievement for quite some time.
